==Korean==

===Noun===
'''나름''' (nareum)
#[[dependence]], [[essence]], [[nature]]

====Derived terms====
*[[사람]] 나름 (saram nareum) dependence on personality
*[[하기]] 나름 (hagi nareum) dependence on what or how to do

====Related terms====
*[[나다]] (nada) to [[arise]], [[become]], [[come out]] 
*[[나오다]] (naoda) to [[appear]], [[come out]], [[emerge]]
*[[나타나다]] (natanada) to [[appear]], [[come out]], [[emerge]]
*[[일어나다]] (ilEnada) to [[arise]], [[occur]]
*[[태어나다]] (taeEonada) to be [[born]] 
: cf. Latin [[nasci]], [[natus]]; Slovene [[narava]] 
*[[낳다]] (nahda) to [[give birth]], [[yield]]

